ce, he was quite interested, though.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubaldisking.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Baldisking</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 26<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/21/02 11:11:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1427.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_cooldude.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Why petition?</span><hr size=1> I do not petition names.  If someone wishes to create silly names, it is up to them.  I only petition KS'ing and training.  I have only petitioned once in 40 levels on this server.  I have petitioned about 4 or 5 times ever ... most of those to get me out from underneath the scarlet desert floor when Verant bugs me on zone in or somesuch!<br>
